tence\": \"On Australia's mistake which helped them secure bronze, Harper added: 'When it's tight like that, we knew that they had to falter a bit.\", \"from\": 1523, \"to\": 1659, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1526, \"end\": 1535, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australia_national_rugby_union_team\", \"score\": 0.8767810703144884, \"rank\": 0.04824021216971269, \"text\": \"Australia\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australia_national_rugby_union_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australia_national_rugby_union_team\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"bronze\", \"from\": 1571, \"to\": 1577}, {\"ngram\": \"Harper\", \"from\": 1579, \"to\": 1585}, {\"ngram\": \"a bit\", \"from\": 1653, \"to\": 1658}]}, {\"sentence\": \"For them to feel the pressure and drop that dive meant that we come away with the bronze medal so we could not be more pleased.\", \"from\": 1661, \"to\": 1788, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the pressure\", \"from\": 1678, \"to\": 1690}, {\"ngram\": \"that dive\", \"from\": 1700, \"to\": 1709}, {\"ngram\": \"the bronze medal\", \"from\": 1739, \"to\": 1755}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Mew Jensen, meanwhile, paid an emotional tribute to the late Jenkins, who died aged just 31 after coaching Team GB's Olympic squad in Tokyo three years ago.\", \"from\": 1790, \"to\": 1946, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1897, \"end\": 1904, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Team_GB\", \"score\": 0.8351514998328787, \"rank\": 0.19738752508604773, \"text\": \"Team GB\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Team_GB\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Team_GB\"}, {\"begin\": 1924, \"end\": 1929, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo\", \"score\": 0.9996592644102388, \"rank\": 0.00034035823357904247, \"text\": \"Tokyo\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo\"}], \"noun_phrases\"